KELLER WILLIAMS REALTY AT THE LAKES

data.description: Desirable gated golf course community in Davenport, FL. This home that sits on almost 1/4-acre, stainless steel appliances only 3 years old, and A/C is 4 years old. The spacious master suite features a large walk-in closet, dual sinks, a garden tub, and a separate shower. Just off the living room is a bedroom/office with a picture window letting in plenty of natural light. On the other side of the home, there are two additional bedrooms and a full bath. Lots of closet space and additional shelving make storage a breeze in this home! Expansive sliders open to the screened lanai which overlooks your very private backyard with plenty of room for a private pool. Amenities include a pool, tennis, and pickle ball courts.
